Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.92,0:02:02.51,OP2-CN,,0,0,0,,	{\blur1\fad(100,500)}坚定的誓言紧握手心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.65,0:02:17.90,OP2-CN,,0,0,0,,	{\blur1\fad(100,100)}一心追求奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.90,0:02:23.08,OP2-CN,,0,0,0,,	{\blur1\fad(100,100)}在无尽的黑暗中彷徨
