Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.48,0:02:59.86,OP2-CN,,0,0,0,,	{\blur1\fad(100,100)}若能变得更强一点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.07,0:03:03.57,OP2-CN,,0,0,0,,	{\blur1\fad(100,100)}眼前的这个天空
